author: AP
title: WNBA postpones start of season this month because of virus
description: The WNBA has postponed the start of its season because of the coronavirus pandemic
content:
NEW YORK (AP) — The WNBA has postponed the start of its season because of the coronavirus pandemic, with no indication when play would begin.
